---
title: Golden Crumbed Chicken Schnitzels with Kumara Wedges & Creamy Rainbow Slaw
description: Golden crusted chicken schnitzels get a boost of flavour with a moreish spice blend! Serve up a side of kumara wedges plus a crisp and colourful slaw for a bright and tasty dinner that brings fun and flavour to the table.
